ont-size: 14px; font-weight: 900\">02</p>\n        <h2 style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 23px; line-height: 1.22; word-break: keep-all\">편집 가능한 구조</h2>\n        <p style=\"margin: 12px 0 0; color: #56606c; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all\">텍스트, 이미지, 버튼, 블록을 안정적인 ID로 추적합니다.</p>\n      </article>\n      <article style=\"min-height: 150px; border: 3px solid #171717; border-radius: 22px; background: #eaf6f3; padding: 22px; box-shadow: 10px 10px 0 rgba(23, 23, 23, 0.08)\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px; color: #2f9f8f; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 900\">03</p>\n        <h2 style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 23px; line-height: 1.22; word-break: keep-all\">한국어 디자인 감각</h2>\n        <p style=\"margin: 12px 0 0; color: #56606c; font-size: 16px; word-break: keep-all\">문장 길이, 행간, 여백을 한국어 제품 화면에 맞춥니다.</p>\n      </article>\n    </section>\n  </section>\n  \n  \n</main>\n</body>\n</html>"}],"devModeReports":[],"devCodeSnippets":[],"readyForDevMarkers":[],"versionDiffs":[],"assetDownloads":[],"exportArtifacts":[{"id":"artifact_1isyg6n","jobId":"export_9nqzdw","kind":"mp4","filename":"animation.mp4","mimeType":"video/mp4","bytes":32,"sha256":"de17900c6e6225de65eec7b1970c03636113a98dc8a9c0e9ea5e937fa7ad32f8","sourceRevision":"rev_1guraue","viewport":"desktop","filePath":"/Users/a0000/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/Desktop/dev/codex-design/.tmp-export-worker/phase-10/animation.mp4","diagnostics":["worker-created","animation-mp4","ffmpeg-bundled:/Users/a0000/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/Desktop/dev/codex-design/node_modules/.pnpm/@ffmpeg-installer+ffmpeg@1.1.0/node_modules/@ffmpeg-installer/darwin-arm64/ffmpeg"],"createdAt":"2026-04-29T00:00:00.000Z:mp4"},{"id":"artifact_ffs5au","jobId":"export_2pg7se","kind":"gif","filename":"animation.gif","mimeType":"image/gif","bytes":43,"sha256":"e4c8efe0cd4a34ef45c313760fe5bd92c0d0d61cf444ca99d53519d9d3657608","sourceRevision":"rev_1guraue","viewport":"desktop","filePath":"/Users/a0000/Library/Mobile Documents/